WEBVTT

00:02.302 --> 00:06.739
THE SKIN GRAFT WILL HAVE HEALED
ENTIRELY BY NOW.

00:15.682 --> 00:17.583
MR. AND MRS. HEIN,

00:17.585 --> 00:22.254
I AM SORRY TO SAY
YOUR SON SEEMS TO HAVE
"ORLANDO BLOOM SYNDROME."

00:22.256 --> 00:23.922
ONE MINUTE HE'S HERE,

00:23.924 --> 00:26.425
AND THEN IT'S LIKE,
"AAH! WHERE'D HE GO?"

00:26.427 --> 00:27.760
[ LAUGHS ]

00:27.762 --> 00:30.429
I'M VERY SORRY
FOR YOUR LOSS.

00:30.431 --> 00:32.998
[ MONITOR BEEPING ]
COME ON.

00:33.000 --> 00:35.467
COME ON.

00:35.469 --> 00:37.202
[ FLATLINE ]

00:37.204 --> 00:39.772
NOOOOOOOOOOO!

00:39.774 --> 00:41.040
AAH! AAAH!
BLAKE!

00:41.042 --> 00:42.341
BLAKE, WAKE UP.

00:42.343 --> 00:43.976
YOU WERE HAVING
A NIGHTMARE.

00:43.978 --> 00:45.444
OH, THANK GOD.

00:45.446 --> 00:48.514
[ BOTH LAUGH ]

00:49.249 --> 00:51.183
CHET! CHET!
HUH?

00:51.185 --> 00:53.786
YOU WERE LAUGHING
IN YOUR SLEEP.
OH.

00:53.788 --> 00:55.020
WHILE YOU WERE DRIVING!

00:55.022 --> 00:57.156
[ BOTH SCREAMING, HORN BLARES ]

00:57.158 --> 00:58.991
CAT, CAT!
WHAT?

00:58.993 --> 01:01.427
YOU WERE SCREAMING
IN YOUR SLEEP.

01:01.429 --> 01:03.962
WHILE WE WERE HAVING SEX.

01:03.964 --> 01:05.931
NOT COOL.

01:05.933 --> 01:08.000
WELL, LET ME
MAKE IT UP TO YOU...

01:08.002 --> 01:08.634
OH.

01:08.636 --> 01:09.802
BLAKE!
AH.

01:09.804 --> 01:11.336
YOU WERE MOANING
IN YOUR SLEEP.

01:11.338 --> 01:14.373
WHILE YOU WERE SUPPOSED TO BE
PERFORMING SURGERY!

01:14.375 --> 01:16.675
OH.
[ FLATLINE ]

01:16.677 --> 01:18.710
NOOOOOOOOOOO!

01:18.712 --> 01:21.146
WAIT A MINUTE.
YOU KNOW WHAT?
THIS IS A DREAM.

01:21.148 --> 01:23.949
YEAH. SOMETHING'S GONNA
WAKE ME UP IN A FEW SECONDS.

01:23.951 --> 01:24.650
WATCH THIS.

01:24.652 --> 01:26.285
[ FLATLINE CONTINUES ]

01:26.287 --> 01:27.986
COUPLE SECONDS.

01:29.956 --> 01:31.657
NAH, IT'S REAL.
THIS KID'S DEAD.

01:31.659 --> 01:34.593
TIME OF DEATH -- 11:20 A.M.

01:34.595 --> 01:37.696
[ MID-TEMPO MUSIC PLAYS ]

01:39.099 --> 01:41.300
WHY DOES THIS
KEEP HAPPENING TO ME?

01:41.302 --> 01:42.568
WELL, I'M NO DOCTOR,

01:42.570 --> 01:44.536
BUT MAYBE YOU SHOULD CUT BACK
ON THE CARBS.

01:44.538 --> 01:46.405
P.S., I AM A DOCTOR.

01:46.407 --> 01:48.941
[ LAUGHTER ]

01:50.743 --> 01:52.678
Man: AND CUT! ALL RIGHT.
[ BELL RINGS ]

01:52.680 --> 01:54.079
YES, GOOD, GOOD, GOOD.

01:54.081 --> 01:56.215
THAT'S A WRAP, EVERYBODY.
THAT'S IT FOR THE DAY.

01:56.217 --> 01:57.616
AND I GOT YOU OUT IN TIME.

01:57.618 --> 02:00.285
ONLY ONE MORE HOUR TILL
YOUR BIG PHOTO SHOW, MY FRIEND.

02:00.287 --> 02:01.920
THANK YOU, MR. WAIN.

02:01.922 --> 02:05.023
WHY ARE YOU HAVING
YOUR PHOTO SHOW HERE
AT THE SOUND STAGES?

02:05.025 --> 02:07.626
IT WAS FREE AND EASY,
LIKE ART.

02:07.628 --> 02:10.929
EXCEPT MY ART IS DIFFICULT
AND VERY EXPENSIVE.

02:10.931 --> 02:13.599
HEY, LISTEN, DAVID,
WILL YOU TEXT ME THE
ADDRESS TO THE PHOTO SHOW?

02:13.601 --> 02:16.068
OH, NO, NO, NO, NO.
IT'S JUST HAPPENING
RIGHT HERE ON SET.

02:16.070 --> 02:19.071
OKAY, THEN TEXT ME THAT.
JUST COME RIGHT HERE
WHERE WE'RE STANDING
RIGHT NOW IN AN HOUR.

02:19.073 --> 02:21.540
JUST INCLUDE ALL THAT
IN THE TEXT.

02:21.542 --> 02:22.741
SO WHAT'S THE DRESS CODE?

02:22.743 --> 02:24.343
SHOES, SOCKS, THE WORKS.

02:24.345 --> 02:25.511
HMM. I'VE GOT THAT.

02:25.513 --> 02:27.279
CAN I BRING MY MOM?

02:30.850 --> 02:31.984
YES.

02:31.986 --> 02:34.786
♪♪

02:34.788 --> 02:36.989
SOME OF THE PEOPLE
I WORK WITH!

02:36.991 --> 02:39.992
THANK YOU AND YOU'RE WELCOME
FOR COMING VERY MUCH.

02:39.994 --> 02:41.793
I HOPE YOU LIKE HAUNTING IMAGES.

02:41.795 --> 02:43.462
WELL, EVEN IF YOUR PHOTOS
ARE TERRIBLE,

02:43.464 --> 02:46.465
TO HAVE THE NERVE TO MONOPOLIZE
OUR PERSONAL TIME LIKE THIS

02:46.467 --> 02:47.866
IS A REAL TRIUMPH.

02:47.868 --> 02:49.935
OH, THANK YOU,
MR. SPLORN.
EXCUSE ME.

02:49.937 --> 02:52.137
I'D LIKE TO FORMALLY WELCOME
ALL OF YOU

02:52.139 --> 02:55.073
TO THE PRIVATE,
EXCLUSIVE SHOWING

02:55.075 --> 02:58.544
OF "THROUGH THE EYES
OF A FALCON."

02:58.546 --> 02:59.745
I'M PAULA REILLY.

02:59.747 --> 03:01.747
I'M FROM
THE MATTHEW KREETEE GALLERY,

03:01.749 --> 03:03.215
BUT I WANT TO SAY
MORE IMPORTANTLY

03:03.217 --> 03:07.486
THAT I AM A <i> HUGE,</i>
LONG-TERM, DIE-HARD FAN

03:07.488 --> 03:08.987
OF "CHILD'S HOSPITABLE."

03:08.989 --> 03:12.357
I MEAN, I WOULD WATCH ANYTHING
WITH MARK SPLORN.

03:12.359 --> 03:15.494
MARK, I WANT TO MAKE OUT
WITH YOUR DING-DONG.

03:15.496 --> 03:16.929
OH.
OKAY.
WHO DOESN'T?

03:16.931 --> 03:18.864
AND WHO IS
THIS LOVELY LADY?

03:18.866 --> 03:21.867
OH, I'M DIXIE'S MOTHER.
IT IS SUCH AN HONOR TO MEET YOU.

03:21.869 --> 03:23.068
I HAVE SO MANY PHOTOS.

03:23.070 --> 03:24.570
I'VE ALWAYS --
Mark: UH, GERALDINE?

03:24.572 --> 03:26.738
YOU KNOW,
LET'S JUST HEAD INSIDE.

03:26.740 --> 03:28.273
I'M SORRY.
I DIDN'T MEAN TO GET IN THE WAY.

03:28.275 --> 03:30.075
WILL YOU STOP EMBARRASSING
MY MOM?!

03:30.077 --> 03:33.011
I WASN'T, I JUST --
UGH. NEVER MIND.

03:33.013 --> 03:35.948
NOW WHO IS READY
TO SEE SOME ART?!

03:35.950 --> 03:37.115
YES.
FOLLOW ME.

03:37.117 --> 03:39.851
-LET'S GO.
-NO, IT'S NOT OKAY.

03:39.853 --> 03:42.454
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

03:51.364 --> 03:53.065
-WHAT IS THAT?
-I DON'T UNDERSTAND.

03:53.067 --> 03:55.634
Falcon: SOMETIMES
THE MAGICAL SECRET WORLD

03:55.636 --> 03:57.869
LIES RIGHT BENEATH YOUR NOSES.

03:57.871 --> 04:00.038
LIKE MUSTACHES.

04:00.040 --> 04:02.674
Woman: THESE ARE JUST PICTURES
HE TOOK ON SET.

04:02.676 --> 04:04.710
UH, PARDON ME.
SHE -- SHE'S FINE.

04:04.712 --> 04:07.079
LOOK, I KNOW IT'S HARD
WHEN EVERYONE'S DRINKING.

04:07.081 --> 04:09.748
JUST REMEMBER. IF YOU GET
TO 12 MONTHS' SOBRIETY,

04:09.750 --> 04:11.116
YOU KNOW WHAT THE DEAL IS.

04:11.118 --> 04:13.218
I'M TAKING YOU OUT
TO A PASTA DINNER.

04:13.220 --> 04:16.321
SIDE DISHES,
THE WHOLE NINE YARDS.

04:16.322 --> 04:17.522
[ CHUCKLES ]

04:17.524 --> 04:19.658
LYNN? WHERE'D YOU GO?

04:19.660 --> 04:23.762
WHERE'D YOU GO?
LYNN? HONEY?

04:26.132 --> 04:29.234
I DON'T REMEMBER
POSING FOR THIS SHOT.

04:29.236 --> 04:31.603
ME EITHER.

04:31.605 --> 04:33.338
OH! OH!

04:33.340 --> 04:34.573
OH! SORRY.

04:34.575 --> 04:36.074
OH, BOY.

04:36.076 --> 04:38.844
OH, MY GOD, I AM SICK
OF YOUR RUDENESS TO MY MOM.

04:38.846 --> 04:40.679
ALL I SAID WAS,
"OH, BOY."

04:40.681 --> 04:42.781
YEAH, BUT IF YOU'RE
NOT GONNA BE NICE, THEN
YOU MIGHT AS WELL

04:42.783 --> 04:45.183
FIND SOMEWHERE ELSE
TO STAY FOR THE ENTIRE
MONTH THAT SHE'S HERE.

04:45.185 --> 04:47.886
FINE! IF THIS IS THE WAY
YOU'RE GONNA ACT, I'LL
JUST STAY IN A HOTEL.

04:47.888 --> 04:49.488
GREAT. I HAVE AN UPGRADE
CODE AT THE LA QUINTA INN.

04:49.490 --> 04:51.723
I SUGGEST YOU USE IT.
CAN I GET THE CODE?

04:51.725 --> 04:55.460
YEAH. YOU CALL THE RESERVATION
LINE AND IT'S "Q27T29."
DO I USE YOUR NAME?

04:55.462 --> 04:57.529
IT'S UNDER MY LEGAL NAME --
CYNTHIA QUELSON.

04:57.531 --> 04:59.131
CAN I BORROW
YOUR PHONE?!

04:59.133 --> 05:00.899
YES! BUT IT'S LOW ON BATTERY
SO PLUG IT IN WHEN YOU'RE DONE!

05:00.901 --> 05:02.367
I HAVE A LIGHTNING CABLE!

05:02.369 --> 05:04.803
GOOGLE, FIND LA QUINTA INN
NEAR ME.

05:04.805 --> 05:06.338
[ Slurred ] DAVID,
STOP BUMPING INTO ME!

05:06.340 --> 05:08.407
WHAT ARE YOU TALKING ABOUT?
I WAS JUST STANDING RIGHT HERE.

05:08.409 --> 05:10.309
DON'T TELL ME HOW TO WALK.
[ SCOFFS ]

05:10.311 --> 05:13.211
I'M HAVING A GOOD TIME.
THAT'S ALL, OKAY?

05:13.213 --> 05:15.113
LYNN, HAVE --
HAVE YOU BEEN DRINKING?

05:15.115 --> 05:16.581
HAVE <i> YOU</i> BEEN DRINKING?

05:16.583 --> 05:21.486
NO, I'M STAYED SOBER SINCE REHAB
ENDED EVER SINCE.

05:27.927 --> 05:29.361
UH. WHAT THE...?

05:29.363 --> 05:31.697
GOOD GOD,
YOU <i> HAVE</i> BEEN DRINKING.

05:31.699 --> 05:33.732
OKAY, FINE.

05:33.734 --> 05:35.133
OKAY?
I'VE BEEN DRINKING.

05:35.135 --> 05:38.170
I LOVE ALCOHOL.
BUT WHAT HAPPENED TO YOU, DAVID?

05:38.172 --> 05:40.739
HOW COME YOU'RE
SUCH A POOP POOPER?

05:40.741 --> 05:42.741
WHEN DID THAT HAPPEN?
WHEN?

05:42.743 --> 05:45.377
EVERYBODY, PLEASE JOIN ME
FOR PHASE TWO.

05:45.379 --> 05:47.179
AND FOR THE RECORD,
YOU ALL ARE THE FIRST

05:47.181 --> 05:52.117
TO BE LAYING EYES
ON THESE PHOTO...GRIEFS.

05:52.119 --> 05:54.219
FOLLOW ME.
DON'T --
STOP TOUCHING ME.

05:54.221 --> 05:59.858
I CALL THIS COLLECTION
"MORE PHOTOS."

05:59.860 --> 06:02.327
YOU KNOW, I TOOK
ALL THESE PHOTOS THIS MORNING.

06:02.329 --> 06:04.129
Paula: PLEASE JOIN ME
IN THE COURTYARD

06:04.131 --> 06:06.031
FOR FURTHER PENETRATION
INTO THE HUMAN SOUL.

06:06.033 --> 06:07.499
HEY, WAIT.
WHAT THE...?

06:07.501 --> 06:09.935
THAT'S -- THAT'S NOT BOOZE.
THAT'S APPLE CIDER.

06:09.937 --> 06:11.837
[ Slurred ] NO, NO.

06:11.839 --> 06:15.107
NO, IT'S NOT.
I'M SUPER-DRUNK.

06:15.109 --> 06:17.676
WHY DID YOU LIE ABOUT
GOING OFF THE WAGON?

06:17.678 --> 06:19.711
NO, PSSSSH!

06:19.713 --> 06:22.347
MNH-MNH. NO.

06:25.385 --> 06:26.451
[ SIGHS ]

06:26.453 --> 06:28.353
DAVID, NOBODY WANTS
A SOBER ACTRESS.

06:28.355 --> 06:30.355
EVERYBODY WANTS
THE SLOPPY TRAIN WRECK.

06:30.357 --> 06:33.058
SO YOU PRETENDED
TO START DRINKING AGAIN?

06:33.060 --> 06:35.460
YEAH, I DIDN'T WANT
TO SEEM LIKE A SQUARE.

06:35.462 --> 06:39.831
YOU MAY BE A SQUARE,
BUT YOU FRAME ME PERFECTLY.

06:39.833 --> 06:42.200
OH, DAVID.

06:43.202 --> 06:46.138
BUT I CAN NEVER FORGIVE YOU
FOR LYING, SO IT'S OVER.

06:46.140 --> 06:47.572
WH--
THAT'S IT.

06:47.574 --> 06:48.940
WH--
THAT'S IT.

06:48.942 --> 06:50.942
THAT'S IT.

06:50.944 --> 06:53.011
Falcon: PHASE THREE.

06:53.013 --> 06:55.213
THE FINAL PHASE.

06:55.215 --> 06:57.115
AND THEN THERE'S ONE MORE
AFTER THAT.

06:58.651 --> 07:02.654
-UH, HOLY CHRISTMAS.
-WAIT. COME LOOK AT THIS.

07:02.656 --> 07:04.656
YOU HAVE A FACE
ON YOUR BACK.

07:04.658 --> 07:06.658
WHAT YOU JUST SAID
SOUNDS ABSURD.
NO, WAIT, WAIT, WAIT.

07:06.660 --> 07:08.460
I THINK I'VE ONLY EVER SEEN YOU
FACE FORWARD.

07:08.462 --> 07:10.095
I DON'T THINK
I'VE EVER SEEN YOUR BACK.

07:10.097 --> 07:12.364
MARK, MARK,
THIS IS PHOTOSHOP, OBVIOUSLY.

07:12.366 --> 07:15.167
NO, NO, NO, NO, HE ALWAYS
IS MAKING ME STAGE THE SCENES

07:15.169 --> 07:16.601
SO WE DON'T SEE HIS BACK.

07:16.603 --> 07:18.570
OKAY, OKAY, OKAY!

07:18.572 --> 07:19.871
ALL RIGHT?

07:19.873 --> 07:22.774
I HAVE A CREATURE
GROWING OUT OF MY BACK.

07:22.776 --> 07:24.810
[ GASPS ]
IS IT ALIVE?

07:24.812 --> 07:26.478
SORT OF. SORT OF.

07:26.480 --> 07:28.980
YEAH, I MEAN IT MOVES ITS MOUTH
A LITTLE BIT.

07:28.982 --> 07:30.315
SO IT CAN TALK?

07:30.317 --> 07:32.451
[ CHUCKLES ] CAN IT TALK?
DID YOU HEAR THAT?

07:32.453 --> 07:34.920
NO! IT CAN'T TALK.
THAT'S RIDICULOUS.

07:34.922 --> 07:37.456
IT CAN SIGH A LITTLE BIT.

07:37.458 --> 07:38.557
IT SIGHS.

07:38.559 --> 07:40.058
DOES HE HAVE A NAME?

07:40.060 --> 07:41.493
TERRY MALONE.

07:41.495 --> 07:42.527
SHOW IT TO US.

07:42.529 --> 07:44.663
SHOW US THE BACK-FACE,
YOU FREAK.

07:44.665 --> 07:47.199
[ ALL SHOUTING ]

07:47.201 --> 07:49.534
OH, I'M --<i> I'M</i> A FREAK?!

07:49.536 --> 07:53.672
BECAUSE MY HALF-ALIVE TWIN
IS GROWING ON MY BACK!

07:53.674 --> 07:57.642
WELL, I GUESS IF THAT'S TRUE,
THEN WE'RE ALL FREAKS.

07:57.644 --> 08:00.011
NO, IT'S JUST YOU
'CAUSE YOU'RE THE ONLY ONE

08:00.013 --> 08:01.746
WITH A HEAD GROWING
OUT OF YOUR BACK.

08:01.748 --> 08:06.785
OKAY, IF YOU GUYS ARE SO
OBSESSED WITH SEEING MY BACK,

08:06.787 --> 08:07.986
I'LL SHOW IT TO YOU...

08:07.988 --> 08:11.056
YES!
...AS I WALK OUT THAT DOOR.

08:11.058 --> 08:13.325
[ MURMURING ]

08:13.327 --> 08:15.760
Man: YEAH. TURN AROUND.
LET'S SEE.

08:15.762 --> 08:19.564
O.M.G.

08:19.566 --> 08:21.032
THERE IT IS.

08:21.034 --> 08:22.701
Falcon: THANKS FOR COMING,
MR. SPINDELL!

08:22.703 --> 08:25.537
AND THANK YOU
FOR COMING, MR. MALONE.

08:25.539 --> 08:26.938
[ Crying ] OH, GOD.

08:26.940 --> 08:28.607
OH, NO, NO, NO, NO.
GERALDINE, IT'S OKAY.

08:28.609 --> 08:29.875
IT'S OVER.

08:29.877 --> 08:31.376
[ SOBBING ]

08:31.378 --> 08:32.611
I AM SORRY.

08:32.613 --> 08:33.812
I'M SORRY.

08:33.813 --> 08:35.813
I WAS WRONG ABOUT YOU.

08:35.816 --> 08:38.015
YOU DO CARE ABOUT MY MOM.

08:38.018 --> 08:40.784
HEY, DIXIE.
TAKE A LOOK AT THESE.

08:40.787 --> 08:42.988
OH, SHIT.

08:44.123 --> 08:45.757
LOOK AT --
WHA?

08:45.759 --> 08:48.193
LOOK AT THAT.
BUT START -- START OVER THERE.

08:48.195 --> 08:50.595
IT REALLY TELLS A STORY.
WHOA.

08:50.597 --> 08:52.664
OH, MY. YOU...

08:52.666 --> 08:54.733
HE'S -- YOU --

08:54.735 --> 08:56.668
OH!

08:56.670 --> 08:58.537
OHH!

08:58.539 --> 09:01.273
YOU -- YOU BASTARD!
NO, NO, NO.

09:01.275 --> 09:03.375
BABY.
AND YOU! SLUT!

09:03.377 --> 09:04.743
AAH!

09:04.745 --> 09:06.511
[ ALL GASP ]

09:06.513 --> 09:12.017
♪ WE DANCED IN THE MOONLIGHT ♪

09:12.019 --> 09:16.154
♪ HELD HANDS IN THE PARK ♪

09:16.156 --> 09:19.958
♪ WE STROLLED BY THE RIVER ♪

09:19.960 --> 09:24.796
♪ AND KISSED IN THE DARK ♪

09:24.798 --> 09:31.136
♪ I NEVER HAD
THE GLOW I FEEL TONIGHT ♪
[ DIXIE SCREECHING ]

09:31.138 --> 09:38.109
♪ IT'S A MIRACLE MOMENT
OF LOVE ♪

09:38.111 --> 09:39.611
THAT'S IT FOR ME.

09:39.613 --> 09:41.580
FALCON, THANK YOU FOR
A TERRIBLE, TERRIBLE NIGHT.

09:41.582 --> 09:44.082
OH, THANK YOU, MR. SPLORN.
THAT'S VERY SWEET OF YOU, AGAIN.

09:44.084 --> 09:45.584
I'M GOING, TOO.

09:45.586 --> 09:48.520
Paula: PHOTOS ARE FOR SALE
IN THE LOBBY, EVERYONE.

09:48.522 --> 09:51.156
WHAT? WHY WOULD WE WANT TO OWN
THOSE PHOTOS?

09:51.158 --> 09:52.591
WELL, IT'S NOT JUST
THE PHOTOS.

09:52.593 --> 09:54.759
IT'S ALSO THE NEGATIVES
AND THE EXISTING PRINTS.

09:54.761 --> 10:00.031
SO THAT THEY'LL NEVER, EVER
BE SEEN BY ANYONE EVER AGAIN.

10:00.033 --> 10:02.734
UH-HUH-HUH.
LOBBY.

10:04.470 --> 10:08.573
I MEAN,
I LIKE ART, SO...
JUST TO BE CLEAR,
WE'RE BEING BLACKMAILED, RIGHT?

10:08.575 --> 10:11.443
♪♪
